    id: "st-1553",
    stem: "A patient undergoing surgery develops malignant hyperthermia. The surgical technologist's FIRST priority is to:",
    options: ["Assist in removing all volatile anesthetic agents and prepare dantrolene sodium (Dantrium) for immediate IV administration", "Apply ice packs directly to the surgical wound to cool the patient", "Increase the electrosurgical unit power to speed up the procedure", "Continue the procedure as planned while the anesthesiologist manages the crisis"],
