    stem: "The surgeon requests oxidized regenerated cellulose (Surgicel) for hemostasis. The surgical technologist should know that Surgicel:",
    options: ["Is an absorbable hemostatic agent that should NOT be used near nerves or in closed spaces due to swelling", "Can be safely used as permanent packing material inside the wound", "Must be moistened with saline before application for maximum effectiveness", "Can be used in combination with thrombin for enhanced hemostatic effect"],
